Brentwood is an affluent neighborhood in the Westside of Los Angeles , California .
It is the home of seven private and two public schools .
Originally part of a Mexican land grant , the neighborhood began its modern development in the 1880s and hosted part of the pentathlon in the 1932 Summer Olympics .
It was the site of the 1994 O.J. Simpson murder case and of a disastrous fire in 1961 .
Brentwood is also home to many celebrities such as actors and actresses .